   168	  embedder model, recovery surface.
   169	- [Reference — Python API](../reference/python-api.md) — full surface.
   170	- [Reference — errors](../reference/errors.md) — 18-leaf taxonomy +
   171	  recovery hints.
   172	- [Reference — CLI](../reference/cli.md) — operator verbs (`doctor`,
   173	  `recover`).

