     8	> parity with the Python SDK. Both bindings cover the same five-verb
     9	> surface and the same error taxonomy, but the TS package shipped its
    10	> first working slice on 2026-04-07 and remains the less-mature option.
    11	> For production pilots, prefer Python. See
