     1	# CLI
     2	
     3	Binary: `fathomdb`. Operator-only in 0.6.0; the CLI does **not**
     4	ship application-surface verbs like `search`, `get`, or `list`. Use
     5	the SDK for those.
     6	
     7	Authoritative spec:
     8	[`dev/interfaces/cli.md`](https://github.com/coreyt/fathomdb/blob/0.6.0-rewrite/dev/interfaces/cli.md);
     9	recovery semantics owned by `dev/design/recovery.md`.
